cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI 

The paper deals with image segmentation and deep learning for vehicle retrieval and re-identification tasks, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning networks also suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.LG). The paper also involves similarity measurement and search, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
